Leqrun i iεeddan εeddan mazal wiyaḍ deffir-nsen.
Ur neẓri d acu i n-ğğan, ur neẓri d acu ara d-ğğen.
Ahat s wayen yellan, ad nefhem acu i d aɣ-yuɣen.
Ahat d ajenwi i aɣ-yezlan, d netta ara aɣ-d-issekren.
Win i aɣ-d-yusan yewwi-d Ṛebbi-s d amεiwen.
Anga i aɣ-d-ufan i aɣ-ğğan wid iruḥen.
Kemmlen i d-yeggran ula d Ṛebbi d ayla-nsen.
Tafat tefrari ɣef mkul lğiha tecreq.
Ccedda tefsi ɣef wid inudan lḥeqq.
Yiwen ur aɣ-d-inni ma ad d-tas nnuba ad nenṭeq.
